TitleEnglish: The Success Of Empyrean Xuan Emperor
SummaryEnglish: Wang Fan, who possesses the Nine Heavens Profound Divine Art of martial arts origin, was originally an ordinary student of the Golden Academy. In order to avenge his brother, he wore the Silver Tiger King mask. Since then,  Put on the mask, He is the King of Silver Tiger. Take off the mask, He is  the ordinary Wang Fan.
